{"tid":513044,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[IOS/AN] Ro:守護永恆的愛 非洲每60秒=歐洲1分鐘","createTime":"2017-12-29T06:45:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T13:10:18.000Z","uid":44627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2fc444f8daf5dc2a4430ed73ec7c7cd5a950128f","tid":513044,"uid":44627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T06:45:18.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/19/221732_9694945e8c618eb16a162e1225257d60.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F19%2F221732_9694945e8c618eb16a162e1225257d60.JPG&h=b35d5c39&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\nQ:用咩模擬器好<br />\nA:夜神 BlueStacks呢兩個都幾好用<br />\n<br />\nQ:咩職勁<br />\nA:課金玩就隻隻都可以玩到好勁.無廢職<br />\n<br />\nQ:點搵錢快<br />\nA:<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推塔 打遺址 打MVP</span></span><br />\n<br />\nQ:扭蛋裝抵唔抵扭?<br />\nA:大部份扭蛋裝都可以幫到你過渡初期大半時間 有加經有加六圍輸出唔低 都幫唔少手,<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不過重點係 扭蛋每日扭一次好.因為每晚會重置. 10貓幣一次.唔好一次扭幾個<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\nQ:點升LV快?<br />\nA:<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">每個城既300詩人 每日5次裂痕任,兩次對抗魔潮任,十次委託任都夠每日2,3個LV 有多時間就掛下材料 寵物冒險都幫到手升下Lv 有時仲一個唔覺意掛到卡片返黎 61lv金字塔2樓 寵物冒險一個鐘22萬經驗左右</span></span><br />\n<br />\nQ:賣卡片好賺定係賣特典好賺?<br />\nA:投資涉及風險,有賺都一定有蝕唔好人講你就跟住ALL IN.卡片炒賣真係睇果期需要乜<br />\n<br />\nQ:駛唔駛壓等?<br />\nA:唔洗<br />\n<br />\nQ:入公會重唔重要?<br />\nA:<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好撚重要 用黎升星盤</span></span><br />\n<br />\n諗到大家可以之後再補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n祝大家掛到好寶"},{"pid":"05fbaecba34d15fe615be0e358ec738d45b7b077","tid":513044,"uid":44627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T06:45:54.000Z","msg":"屌 漏左(7)係TOPIC度"},{"pid":"cd50422582ab43aeb77afeca4a07f49354232eb2","tid":513044,"uid":44627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep